snippet.title: Panda's Village Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/22...

Panda's Village is a real-time strategy and survival game, where you build and upgrade houses, defenses, and stores, fight fierce monkeys, purchase and upgrade weapons and magic and customize your panda. Your goal is to save the village's Capitol at all costs! If you die, you start over.
